WEBVTT

00:00:06.911 --> 00:00:09.906
Our story is about a girl named Iris.

00:00:09.930 --> 00:00:12.132
Iris is very sensitive.

00:00:12.156 --> 00:00:13.336
(Bird cawing)

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:15.621
So much that she is always in tears.

00:00:16.998 --> 00:00:18.546
She cries when she's sad,

00:00:20.002 --> 00:00:21.512
when she's happy,

00:00:21.836 --> 00:00:22.924
(Godzilla roars)

00:00:23.085 --> 00:00:25.681
and even tears up
when things just get to her.

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:31.339
She has special lacrimal glands
to make new tears